## Closing Thoughts

This is a strong idea with clear product-market fit potential. The thesis (MMO grinders overlap with weightlifters) is specific and testable. The prototype already exists and works. The tools to ship quickly are available.

The only way to fail is to not ship.

Focus on:
1. Getting it live with basic functionality
2. Making it look game-like enough to match the concept
3. Putting it in front of 100 real users
4. Listening to what they do, not just what they say

Everything else is details.

The niche is real. The timing is right. The execution is yours.

Now go make some MMO grinders stronger.

